message.content:
cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel mobile rescue robot and evaluates its performance in terms of task accomplishment and safety. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the robot is equipped with an immersive stereoscopic teleperception, which involves computer vision techniques. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the teleoperation control and the comparison of different teleperception methods. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the robot uses an approach called "loco-manipulation" to perform the casualty-extraction procedure. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the design and implementation of the mobile rescue robot.
